OL,6,FThree people have died after a fire
OL,7,Fbroke out in the early hours of the
OL,8,Fmorning at a hotel in Scotland, police
OL,9,Fhave confirmed.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FNew County Hotel in Perth shortly after
OL,13,F5am on Monday, with police confirming
OL,14,Fthat a "number of guests" had been
OL,15,Fevacuated from the building.
OL,17,FDeputy First Minister, John Swinney,
OL,18,Fdescribed the fatalities as
OL,19,F"heartbreaking news". The MSP for
OL,20,FPerthshire North, added: "My sympathies
OL,21,Fwith all affected by this tragedy."
OL,3,CThree people dead in fire at hotel in
OL,4,CScotland, police confirm
